<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_swre_tsk_history.SRApprovalHistory</api_name><client_callable>false</client_callable><description>Approval History record should only be created using this Script include method 'createApprovalHistory'</description><name>SRApprovalHistory</name><script><![CDATA[/**
 * Approval History Helper class. Methods in this class should be used to create Approval History records from other applications
 * 
 * @class 
 * @author Gurpreet Matharu [S7DHWK]
 * @memberof global.module:sys_script_include
 */
var SRApprovalHistory = Class.create();
SRApprovalHistory.prototype = /** @lends global.module:sys_script_include.SRApprovalHistory.prototype */ {
	/**
	 * Default initialize method
	 * 
	 * @returns {undefined}
	 */
	initialize: function() {
	},

	/**
	 * Create Approval history record for a Task record
	 * 
	 * @param {String} taskSysId Sys ID of the Task
	 * @param {String} approvalSysId Sys ID of the approval record
	 * @param {String} groupSysId Sys ID of the group if the approval is provided as a group approval
	 * @param {String} taskState Task State in which the approval was provided
	 * @param {String} approvalType Type of approval provided
	 * @param {String} comments Approval or Rejection comments
	 * @returns {String} Sys ID of the approval history record created
	 */
	createApprovalHistory: function (taskSysId, approvalSysId, groupSysId, taskState, approvalType, comments) {
		if (gs.nil(taskSysId)) {
			return;
		}
		if (gs.nil(approvalSysId)) {
			return;
		}

		try {
			var taskApprovalHistoryRec = new GlideRecord('x_swre_tsk_history_approval');
			taskApprovalHistoryRec.initialize();
			taskApprovalHistoryRec.u_task = taskSysId;
			taskApprovalHistoryRec.u_approval = approvalSysId;		
			taskApprovalHistoryRec.u_task_state = taskState;
			if (!gs.nil(groupSysId)) {
				taskApprovalHistoryRec.u_assignment_group = groupSysId;
			}
			if (!gs.nil(approvalType)) {
				taskApprovalHistoryRec.u_approval_type = approvalType;
			}

			if (!gs.nil(comments)) {
				taskApprovalHistoryRec.u_comments = comments;
				taskApprovalHistoryRec.u_user_comments = this._getUserComments(comments);

			}
			taskApprovalHistoryRec.insert();

			var err = taskApprovalHistoryRec.getLastErrorMessage();
			if (!gs.nil(err)) {
				throw err;
			}
			return taskApprovalHistoryRec.getValue('sys_id');
		}
		catch (error) {
			gs.error('Error while creating Approval History record: {0} : {1} : {2} \n{3}', [
				taskSysId, 
				approvalSysId, 
				groupSysId, 
				error
			]);
			return;
		}
	},

	/**
		 * Create the actual user comments by formating the comment
		 * 
		 * @param {String} journalEntry
		 * @returns {String} Actual user comments 
		 */
	_getUserComments: function(journalEntry){
		var journalEntryArray=journalEntry.split('\n\n');
		var ignoreTextArray = [
			'reply from:',
			'Ref:',
			'This e-mail, including attachments, is intended for the person'
		];
		var filteredArray = journalEntryArray.filter(function (emailLine) {
			//gs.info(elm);
			return ignoreTextArray.every(function (ignoreText) {
				return emailLine.indexOf(ignoreText) == -1;
			});
		});
		return filteredArray.join('\n');
	},

	type: 'SRApprovalHistory'
